body:
So I hit level 30 a while ago, and I have played ranked three times so far. I have won one and lost two, and have realized that I should probably not play high risk high reward champions during ranked, at least until my mechanics improve. I like playing mid and top lane, and I was wondering if there were any champions that an unranked pleb like me could play decently. It would be nice if they were kinda forgiving, as I am going to make a lot of mistakes. Please leave some feedback, as I am inexperienced compared to other people.
